sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(Data Scientist)
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant BFF as odh-dashboard BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GenAI as gen-ai BFF<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Pipeline as DS Pipeline API<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8s: Flow 1: User Authentication & Dashboard Access

    Browser->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443)
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS reencrypt
    KRBAC-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OAuth
    Browser->>OAuth: OAuth2 Authorization Code Flow
    OAuth-->>Browser: Bearer Token (cookie)
    Browser->>Route: GET / + Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS reencrypt + Bearer
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: Validate: can list projects?
    KRBAC->>BFF: HTTP/8080 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>K8s: GET /api/status (Bearer user token)
    K8s-->>BFF: User identity + cluster info
    BFF-->>KRBAC: JSON response
    KRBAC-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Browser: Dashboard SPA + user context

    Note over Browser,K8s: Flow 2: Federated Module Loading

    Browser->>Route: GET /_mf/gen-ai/remoteEntry.js
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS reencrypt + Bearer
    KRBAC->>BFF: HTTP/8080 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>GenAI: HTTPS/8143 + x-forwarded-access-token
    GenAI-->>BFF: remoteEntry.js (Module Federation)
    BFF-->>KRBAC: JS response
    KRBAC-->>Browser: Module chunks loaded

    Note over Browser,LlamaStack: Flow 3: Gen AI Inference Request

    Browser->>Route: POST /gen-ai/api/v1/lsd/responses
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS reencrypt + Bearer
    KRBAC->>BFF: HTTP/8080 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>GenAI: HTTPS/8143 + Bearer
    GenAI->>LlamaStack: HTTP/8321 + Bearer<br/>POST /inference/chat
    LlamaStack-->>GenAI: AI Response (streaming)
    GenAI-->>BFF: Response
    BFF-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Browser: JSON AI response

    Note over Browser,Pipeline: Flow 4: Pipeline Run Creation

    Browser->>Route: POST /api/service/pipelines/runs
    Route->>KRBAC: TLS reencrypt + Bearer
    KRBAC->>BFF: HTTP/8080 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>Pipeline: HTTPS/8443 + Bearer (user token)
    Pipeline-->>BFF: Pipeline run created
    BFF-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Browser: Run details

    Note over Browser,K8s: Flow 5: WebSocket Watch (Real-time Updates)

    Browser->>Route: WS Upgrade /wss/k8s/api/v1/pods?watch=true
    Route->>KRBAC: WSS/8443 + Bearer
    KRBAC->>BFF: WS/8080 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF->>K8s: WSS/6443 + Bearer (base64 subprotocol)
    loop Watch Events
        K8s-->>BFF: Event: ADDED/MODIFIED/DELETED
        BFF-->>KRBAC: WS frame
        KRBAC-->>Browser: Real-time update
    end
